    This class contains methods which parse data in MzML format from File, Path or InputStream
    Scans and Chromatograms will be parsed, and the values pre-loaded when the Predicate is passed. Other Scans and Chromatograms can be loaded on demand if the source is a File, whereas, they will be dropped if the source is an InputStream
